3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes an AI-based approach to model geo-spatial data and learn spatial correlations automatically. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper deals with the estimation of housing prices using multiple sources of data, including satellite imagery, which can be seen as a form of information retrieval.
